Distinctness.Description: Distinctness subscale from Morningness-Eveningness-Stability-Scale improved (MESSi) questionnaire (Randler et al., 2016)

Eveningness.Description: Eveningness subscale from Morningness-Eveningness-Stability-Scale improved (MESSi) questionnaire (Randler et al., 2016)

Morning_affect.Description: Morning affect subscale from Morningness-Eveningness-Stability-Scale improved (MESSi) questionnaire (Randler et al.,  2016)

SPSRQ_SP.Description: Sensitivity to punishment subscale from Sensitivity to Punishment and Sensitivity to Reward Questionnaire (SPSRQ; (Torrubia et al., 2001)

SPSRQ_SR.Description: Sensitivity to reward subscale from Sensitivity to Punishment and Sensitivity to Reward Questionnaire (SPSRQ; (Torrubia et al., 2001)

NEO_FFI_neuroticism_score.Description: Neuroticism subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_neuroticism_stens.Description: Neuroticism subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_extraversion_score.Description: Extraversion subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_extraversion_stens.Description: Extraversion subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_openness_score.Description: Openness subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_openness_stens.Description: Openness subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_agreeableness_score.Description: Agreeableness subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_agreeableness_stens.Description: Agreeableness subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_conscientiousness_score.Description: Conscientiousness subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

NEO_FFI_conscientiousness_stens.Description: Conscientiousness subscale from  NEO-Five Factor Inventory,NEO-FFI, (Jr & McCrae, 1992)

GAD_score.Description: Generalized Anxiety Disorder, GAD-7, (Spitzer et al., 2006)

PANAS_PA.Description: Positive affect subscale from Positive and Negative Affect Schedule PANAS, (Crawford & Henry, 2004)

PANAS_NA.Description: Negative affect subscale from Positive and Negative Affect Schedule PANAS, (Crawford & Henry, 2004)

BAS_drive.Description: Behavioral activation system - drive subscale from Behavioral Activation System and Behavioral Inhibition System, BIS/BAS, (Carver & White, 1994;)

BAS_fun.Description: Behavioral activation system - fun Seeking subscale from Behavioral Activation System and Behavioral Inhibition System, BIS/BAS, (Carver & White, 1994;)

BAS_reward.Description: Behavioral activation system - reward responsiveness subscale from Behavioral Activation System and Behavioral Inhibition System, BIS/BAS, (Carver & White, 1994;)

BIS.Description: Behavioral inhibition system - from Behavioral Activation System and Behavioral Inhibition System, BIS/BAS, (Carver & White, 1994;)

ASRS_score.Description: Attention deficit from AAdult ADHD Self-Report Scale, ASRS (Kessler et al., 2005)
